# W-Roster-And-Rebirth — DONE 2026-05-01

Worker brief: replace SKINS catalog with 9-character roster, add roster
picker UI + polished Rebirth-event modal, wire per-character Power and
Cultivate cost ladder.

## Concerns shipped

- **A** `7033340` W-Roster-And-Rebirth A — replace skin catalog with 9-character roster
- **B** `a2008e0` W-Roster-And-Rebirth B — roster picker + Rebirth event modal
- **C** `(this commit)` W-Roster-And-Rebirth C — Cultivate cost ladder + Power readout + done marker

## Catalog summary

9 characters, 25 total Rebirth tiers (catalog in `js/ascend/ascend-skins.js`).

| id                | archetype       | name             | tiers |
|-------------------|-----------------|------------------|------:|
| lantern_acolyte   | schoolgirl      | Lantern Acolyte  | 4 |
| sigil_student     | white_haired    | Sigil Student    | 3 |
| horned_oni        | samurai         | Horned Oni       | 3 |
| paper_priest      | jiangshi        | Paper Priest     | 3 |
| silent_seer       | seated_grim     | Silent Seer      | 2 |
| scythe_widow      | hooded_reaper   | Scythe Widow     | 3 |
| ash_brawler       | afro_brawler    | Ash Brawler      | 2 |
| fox_kabuki        | fox_mask        | Fox Kabuki       | 3 |
| cap_apprentice    | cap_boy         | Cap Apprentice   | 2 |

Default unlocked: lantern_acolyte at tier 1. Others gated by IAP cost
(60–500 diamonds) and stage-clear progression (Rebirth tier gate).

## Files touched

- `js/ascend/ascend-skins.js` — SKINS → CHARACTERS catalog, new API
  (list, get, setActive, currentTier, tryUnlock, tryRebirth, rebirthCost,
  activeBonus, activePower). Legacy AscendSkins aliases preserved.
- `js/ascend/ascend-rebirth.js` (NEW) — full-screen Rebirth modal with
  golden-pulsing border, in-place 1.2s portrait crossfade through a
  flash burst, sequenced reward chips (180ms stagger), Cultivate /
  Continue buttons.
- `js/ascend/ascend-render.js` — 3-col TAP-TO-PLAY roster picker
  (active checkmark + scale-bounce on tap), HUD power readout
  annotated with active character tier + next-tier marker / cultivate
  cost.
- `js/core/wg-state.js` — initial state migrated to activeCharacter +
  ownedCharacters + characterTiers + highestStageCleared.
  recomputePower delegates to AscendChars.activePower().
- `js/duel/duel-roster.js` — opponent skin pool drawn from new 9-char
  catalog.
- `js/wg-game.js` — finishHunt bumps highestStageCleared on cleared
  and routes through AscendRebirth.maybeShow before HuntResults.
- `index.html` — ascend-rebirth.js added to module loader.
- `MobileGameResearch/wood-siege/SPEC.md` — §16 entries crossed off,
  §18 changelog v0.16 entry added.

## Cultivate cost ladder

`WG.AscendChars.rebirthCost(charId)` resolves the next-tier cost from
`CULTIVATE_LADDER = { 2: 800, 3: 2880, 4: 14400 }`, with a `power × 12`
fallback for any future tier 5+. Tier 3's 2880 anchors SPEC §8's
quoted Cultivate cost.

## Verified live

Tested in-browser at the wraithgrove preview server (port 3996):

- Picker renders 9 tiles, 1 active (golden border + ✓), 8 locked with
  diamond costs. TAP TO PLAY label only shows on owned non-active.
- Rebirth modal shows when `highestStageCleared >= next.requiresStageClear`.
- Cultivate flow at tier 1 → 2: coins 5000 → 2120 (-2880 wait that's
  wrong for tier 2 → corrected to 800 in this commit). Diamonds +100.
  Hammers (craftFragments) +10. characterTiers.lantern_acolyte = 2.
- isEligible() returns null at max tier and when stage gate not met.
- HUD power readout shows live "Tier N ready · Cultivate Y🪙" when
  rebirth is available, "Tier N locked · clear stage X" otherwise.
- recomputePower returns 208 base / 268 with tier-2 active (correctly
  picks up `WG.AscendChars.activePower()`).

## Out of scope (follow-up workers)

- Per-character sprite draws — `drawAnimeGirl` is still the schoolgirl
  tier-1 render for everyone. Each character + tier deserves its own
  pixel art draw. Stub portraits use tier color/accent for now.
- Stage-clear free reward grant — currently rewards (100💎 + 10🔨) are
  granted only when player commits Cultivate. Could grant on stage
  clear regardless of cultivation, depending on real Wood Siege flow.
- Ad-watch reward boost — Wood Siege offers a 2× rewards ad-watch on
  Rebirth events; not implemented here.
- Per-character Rebirth-tier portrait crossfade uses two stub div
  shapes. Once real sprites land, swap the stub portrait builders for
  the real character art.
